headline: Lower interest rates could boost these stocks & sectors
summary: Miramar Capital co-founder and senior portfolio manager, Max Wasserman, joins Morning Brief host Julie Hyman to discuss portfolio diversification and which stocks and sectors are poised to benefit as interest rates continue to come down. headline: The Home Depot Foundation invests an additional $30 million to help thousands of veterans access, stay in homes
summary: Ahead of Veterans Day, The Home Depot Foundation has invested more than $30 million in new grants to help thousands of veterans secure and maintain safe, accessible housing through critical home repairs, smart home modifications and programs for those exiting homelessness. With these 44 grants to veteran service organizations, the Foundation marches closer toward its pledge to invest $750 million in veteran causes by 2030.
